TITLE: Installing Semi Design UI Library
DESCRIPTION: Commands to install the Semi Design UI library using npm, yarn, or pnpm package managers.
SOURCE: https://github.com/DouyinFE/semi-design/blob/main/content/start/getting-started/index-en-US.md#2025-04-12_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
