TITLE: Syncing Dark Mode with System Preferences in Semi Design
DESCRIPTION: Uses the 'prefers-color-scheme' media query to automatically switch between light and dark modes based on system preferences.
SOURCE: https://github.com/DouyinFE/semi-design/blob/main/content/start/dark-mode/index.md#2025-04-12_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
const mql = window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)');

function matchMode(e) {
    const body = document.body;
    if (e.matches) {
        if (!body.hasAttribute('theme-mode')) {
            body.setAttribute('theme-mode', 'dark');
        }
    } else {
        if (body.hasAttribute('theme-mode')) {
            body.removeAttribute('theme-mode');
        }
    }
}

mql.addListener(matchMode);
```

