TITLE: Using Toast with React Context
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use Toast.useToast to create a contextHolder that can access React context.
SOURCE: https://github.com/DouyinFE/semi-design/blob/main/content/feedback/toast/index-en-US.md#2025-04-12_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: jsx
