TITLE: Defining Nav.Sub Component Properties in Markdown
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines the properties for the Nav.Sub subcomponent using a markdown table. It includes properties such as disabled, dropdownProps, dropdownStyle, icon, indent, isCollapsed, isOpen, itemKey, level, maxHeight, text, onMouseEnter, and onMouseLeave.
