DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to use the `compile` function from the `@douyinfe/semi-scss-compile` package to compile SCSS files. It takes an object with `foundationPath`, `themePath`, `iconPath`, `outputPath`, and `isMin` as parameters to define the compilation process.
